程序包 P2V

类 VImg

java.lang.Object
P2V.VObj
P2V.VImg
public class VImg extends VObj
VImg is a class that represents an image visual object in the application. It extends the VObj abstract class and inherits its properties and methods. However, some methods or properties are not available or readonly in VImg, such as Fill, Stro and so on.
作者:
Telsa
